        {
            "title": "兆易創新超額認購逾541倍　GEM新股BBSB超購1萬倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日再有兩隻新股於主板掛牌，分別是紅星冷鏈(01641)和兆易創新(03986)；另有尚有在GEM上市的BBSB(08610)，亦於今日登場。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"BBSB招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/08610.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"BBSB招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/08610.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">BBSB招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在上述3隻新股中，無論是認購超額倍數或暗盤表現，均以土木工程承包商BBSB明顯跑出。該公司公布，公開發售部分超額認購近1.1萬倍，每手4000股，一手中籤率為0.05%，國際發售部分俎輕微超額認購0.01倍。股份以招股範圍下限0.6元定價，集資淨額5000萬元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據輝立交易平台資料，BBSB昨天暗盤收報3.09元，較招價高4.15倍；富途顯示該股暗盤收報2.74元，也高於招股價3.57倍。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於兩隻主板上市新股當中，集資淨額達46.1億元的兆易創新公布，公開發售部分超額認購逾541倍，每手100股，一手中籤率為2%，國際發售部分超額認購近18倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：兆易創新官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250624_FI_source-web_603986-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：兆易創新官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250624_FI_source-web_603986-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：兆易創新官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兆易創新暗盤亦高收，其中輝立交易平台顯示該股暗盤收報226.8元，較招股價高40^；富途交易平台顯示暗盤收報224.8元，也較招股價高38.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紅星冷鏈則公布，公開發售部分超額認購逾2308倍，每手500股，一手中籤率為1%，國際發售部分超額認購0.65倍。股份以12.26元定價，集資淨額約2.5億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"紅星冷鏈官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/HNHXLL-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"紅星冷鏈官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/HNHXLL-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">紅星冷鏈官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">輝立交易平台顯示，紅星冷鏈暗盤收報16.68元，較招股價高36.1%；富途交易平台顯示暗盤收報18.07元，較招股價更高47.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15577340-%e5%85%86%e6%98%93%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e8%b6%85%e9%a1%8d%e8%aa%8d%e8%b3%bc%e9%80%be541%e5%80%8d%e3%80%80gem%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1bbsb%e8%b6%85%e8%b3%bc1%e8%90%ac%e5%80%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/08610-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-13 08:55:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "華潤置地上月合同銷售按年升28.1% 去年累計仍倒退10.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華潤置地(01109)公布，上月實現總合同銷售約410億元(人民幣．下同)，按年增28.1%；涉及樓面167.9萬平方米，亦升29.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"華潤置地官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/01109-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"華潤置地官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/01109-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">華潤置地官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若將2025年全年合計，累計實現合同銷售約2336億元，按年減少10.5%；涉及樓面922.4萬平方米，按年降18.6%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在經常性收入方面，華潤置地上月單月為52.9億元，按夫升0.8%；其中經營性不動產業務租金收入約30.1億元，按年增長9.4%。2025年全年計經常性收入約511.5億元，按年增長6.5%；經營性不動產業務租金收入約329.4億元，按年升12.8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15577561-%e8%8f%af%e6%bd%a4%e7%bd%ae%e5%9c%b0%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8728-1-%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e4%bb%8d%e5%80%92%e9%80%8010-5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230724_FI_source-web_01109-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-13 08:35:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "龍湖2025年合同銷售跌37.54% 上月降逾53%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">龍湖(00960)公布，2025年累計合同銷售631.6億元(人民幣．下同)，較2024年的1011.2億元減少37.54%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：龍湖官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230817_FI_source-web_龍湖-龍湖星河雲河頌.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：龍湖官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230817_FI_source-web_龍湖-龍湖星河雲河頌.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：龍湖官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">單計去年12月，公司實現總合同銷售37.7億元，更較對上年度同期的81.2元跌53.57%；單月實現歸屬公司股東權益合同銷售23.8億元，按年倒退55.93%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至2025年底，龍湖實現經營性收入約267.7億元，按年微增0.22%；其中運營收入約141.9億元，服務收入約125.8億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15577543-%e9%be%8d%e6%b9%962025%e5%b9%b4%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e8%b7%8c37-54-%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e9%99%8d%e9%80%be53",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250512_FI_source-web_00960.jpg.webp",
